<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Campground</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/index.css" >
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/5a891aa92f.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<style>
*{
    margin:0px;
    padding: 0px;
    box-sizing: border-box;

}
body
{
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

.navbar
{
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;
background-color: khaki;
z-index: 100;
position: absolute;

}

.nav-link
{
margin-left: 4vw;
margin-right: 2vw;
color: black;
cursor: pointer;
font-size: .75rem;
font-weight: 600;


}
.navbar-nav
{
display: flex;
justify-content: space-around;
align-items: center;
}

.nav-link:hover
{
text-decoration: none;
color: inherit;
}

.navbar-brand
{
font-size: 1.5rem;
color: black;
cursor: pointer;
text-transform: uppercase;
font-weight: 500;
margin-left: 5vw;
}

.navbar-brand:hover
{
text-decoration: none;
}

.fab
{
   font-size: 1.8rem;
}

.fas
{
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}
.fab:hover
{
color: cyan;
}
.fas:hover{
color: cadetblue;
}
.section{

margin-top:70px;

}

.section-1{

width:100vw;

min-height: 300px;
background: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1458682625221-3a45f8a844c7?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=500&amp;q=60);
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-size: cover;
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
align-items: center;

}
.column-1{
font-weight: 200;
font-size: 6rem;
}
.column-2{

font-style: italic;
color: white;
font-weight: 600;
}

.find{
 display: none;
   transition: display 4s linear 1s;
}

.campground-image{
width: 100%;
height:30vh;
min-height: 220px;

}  
.campground-title{
font-size: 1.1rem;
font-weight: 700;
}
.campground-title:hover{
text-decoration: underline;
color:darkgoldenrod;
cursor: pointer;
}
.campground-row-1{
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;

}
.campground-row-1-item-1{
font-size: .8rem;
text-transform: uppercase;
font-weight: 500;
}
.addcamp-btn{
    width:15vw;height:40px;font-size:1.2rem;text-transform:uppercase;font-style:italic;
    min-width: 160px;
    min-height: 30px;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .column-1{
      font-size:4rem;
  }  
  .column-2{

font-style: italic;
color: white;
font-weight: 600;
font-size: .6rem;
}
.addcamp-btn{
    font-size:.9rem ;
    height: 10px;
}.fas{
    font-size: .8rem;
}
.navbar-brand{
    font-size: 1.1rem;
}
.nav-link{
    font-size: .5rem;

}
.fab{
    font-size:1.1rem;
}

}

</style>

</head>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand  fixed-top">
<a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram" ></i>  YELPCAMP</a>
<ul class="navbar-nav">
<%if(currentUser&&currentUser._id){%>
<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#"> <%-currentUser.username %></a></li>
<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/logout">LogOut<i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt ml-1"></i></a></li>
<%}
else{%>
<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/register"> SIGN UP  <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt ml-1"></i></a></li>
<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/login">LOG IN <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt ml-1"></i></a></li>
<% }%>
</ul>
</nav>

    <section class="section ">
        <%if(success&& success.length>0){%>
            <div class="alert alert-success  container  "  role="alert">
               <%=success%>
            <%}%>  </div>
            <%if(message&& message.length>0){%>
                <div class="alert alert-success  container  "  role="alert">
                   <%=message%>
                <%}%>  </div>
<section class="section-1 ">
    <div class="container text-center">
        
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12  text-dark column-1">YELPCAMP</div>
    <div class="col-12 display-5  column-2">Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit...<span class="btn btn-link "style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;">..To More</span>
        <div class="find">Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source.</div>
        <hr >
    </div>
    <div class="col-12">
        <a href="/campground/new" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary text-center  rounded addcamp-btn  text-light mb-4">Add YelpCamp</a>

    </div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
    </section>
<section class="section-3 container mt-4">
    <div class="row m-2" style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <%campground.forEach(function(campground){%>
        <div class="col-xl-4 col-md-6  col-sm-12  mb-2 ">
            <div class="campground-container border rounded">

                    <img class="campground-image border rounded" src="<%=campground.image%>">

              <div class="mx-1 ">
                 <div class="campground-row-1 my-2">
                     <div class="campground-row-1-item-1">Uploaded By:-</div>
                      <div class="campground-title"><%-campground.author.username%></div>
                 </div>
                      <div class="mb-1"> 
                        <form action="campground/<%=campground._id%>" method="GET">
                      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block "> To know More</button>
                      </form>

             </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
       
                <%})%>
        
        </div>
</section>
<script>
    var find =document.querySelector(".find");
document.querySelector("span").addEventListener("click",
function(){
    find.style.display="contents";
    this.style.display="none";

}


)

</script>

</html>